      <div class="footer-section"><h3>ilovedatabase</h3><p>Your comprehensive resource for mastering database concepts and technologies.</p></div>
      <div class="footer-section"><h4>Blog</h4><ul><li><a href="../../blog/index.html">All Articles</a></li><li><a href="../../contact/contact.html">Contact</a></li></ul></div>
